The commission established pursuant to KRS 91A.350(3) shall be composed of six (6) members from each county to be appointed by the county judge/executive, with the approval of the fiscal court, one (1) of whom shall be a member of the General Assembly in whose district the county or part of the county is located in the following manner:
One (1) commissioner from a list of at least three (3) persons submitted by the local restaurant association or associations;
One (1) commissioner from a list of at least three (3) persons submitted by the local chamber of commerce;
One (1) commissioner by the county judge/executive; and
Two (2) commissioners from a list of at least six (6) persons submitted by the local hotel and motel association or associations.
